{"tid":381630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門今再拒《蘋果》記者入境 又指「對保安穩定構成威脅」","createTime":"2017-08-31T06:06:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T08:53:31.000Z","uid":42374,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"82b21a705ade558417c64567a03a762169328f67","tid":381630,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:06:32.000Z","msg":"澳門早前受到颱風吹襲，釀成多人死傷，政府被批救災不力之餘，更限制澳門記者只准報喜不准報憂。澳門政府繼上周六拒絕《蘋果》2名記者、《香港01》和《南華早報》記者入境採訪災情後，今日再次拒絕《蘋果》攝記入境採訪災後情況。該《蘋果》攝記今早乘船往澳門採訪，但入境時在外港碼頭被扣留，之後記者獲發一張拒絕入境通知書，「罪名」如之前一樣，<span style=\"color: red;\">聲稱記者「對內部保安的穩定構成威脅」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>，需即時遺返香港。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04afd2796748d7c6ac9f9e166c8566c01685e9ee","tid":381630,"uid":42374,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:07:11.000Z","msg":"好大威脅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20a00e93b7839773cd380d01a1de5f27816de5e9","tid":381630,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:08:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d91ec664cbc4dcd955818dcd5469d54da26ae0db","tid":381630,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:11:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無人理"},{"pid":"1bd2745af7a13539a81b7578b0b3f7cd6bbe364e","tid":381630,"uid":36696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:11:47.000Z","msg":"明顯有黑名單啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22b02424c5a57d08f5dadc6d8ba85b3e8001832e","tid":3